Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！ ウッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:52.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平たち）信ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:52.14,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:22:59.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\N（尾平）ウソだろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.09,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You're kidding me, right? Even Qiang Lei...
